   "source": [
    "import seaborn as sns\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "value_counts=titanic_df['Survived'].value_counts()\n",
    "sns.countplot(x=titanic_df['Survived'], palette=['blue', 'orange'])\n",
    "mean = np.mean(value_counts)\n",
    "std_dev = np.std(value_counts)\n",
    "percentiles = np.percentile(value_counts, [25, 50, 75])\n",
    "for container in plt.gca().containers:\n",
    "    plt.gca().bar_label(container, fontsize=12)\n",
    "plt.axhline(mean, color='red', linestyle='dashed', label=f'Mean: {mean:.2f}')\n",
    "plt.axhline(std_dev, color='red', linestyle='dashed', label=f'standard_deviation: {std_dev:.2f}')\n",
    "plt.axhline(percentiles[0], color='green', linestyle='dotted', label=f'25%: {percentiles[0]:.2f}')\n",
    "plt.axhline(percentiles[1], color='purple', linestyle='dashdot', label=f'50%: {percentiles[1]:.2f}')\n",
    "plt.axhline(percentiles[2], color='orange', linestyle='dotted', label=f'75%: {percentiles[2]:.2f}')\n",
    "plt.legend()\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]

    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import seaborn as sns\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "df_encoded = titanic_df.apply(lambda x: x.astype('category').cat.codes if x.dtype == 'object' else x)\n",
    "corr_matrix=df_encoded.corr()\n",
    "plt.figure(figsize=(14,7))\n",
    "sns.heatmap(corr_matrix, annot=True, cmap=\"coolwarm\", fmt=\".2f\", linewidths=0.5)\n",
    "plt.title(\"Correlation Matrix Heatmap\")\n",
    "plt.show()"
